      Hosting Rails Girls
    %p
      Another way to sponsor Rails Girls London is to provide the venue and catering for a future event. We currently run large Workshops, and small Weekly meetings, and the requirements for each differ.
      If you're interested in doing this, please get in touch at railsgirlslondon@gmail.com, and we'll be happy to arrange something.
